      <title>民意调查显示，尽管经济疲软，欧洲央行仍将继续降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/ecb-to-keep-cutting-quarterly-despite-weaker-economy-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项分析师调查显示，欧洲央行不会通过更快降低利率来应对欧元区经济疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/ecb-to-keep-cutting-quarterly-despite-weaker-economy-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
